{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645630/extras/Comp_14.gif?t=1740070277\" /><br><br>In <strong>FEROCIOUS,</strong> your adventure begins after a shipwreck in the uncharted waters of the Pacific Ocean, where you awaken on the shores of a deadly island. Your priority is to <strong>locate your missing brother</strong> but as you venture deeper, it becomes evident that you\u2019re not the only human being around. Mercenaries infest the land, setting the stage for <strong>a game of stealth, strategy, and survival</strong>. Navigate meticulously crafted maps, each offering unique strategies to outmaneuver enemy patrols and encampments.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645630/extras/Comp_15.gif?t=1740070277\" /><br><br>The situation is grim enough without considering the island's prehistoric denizens, that also demand you respect\u2026  As you progress through <strong>FEROCIOUS\u2019 campaign</strong>, you will get to understand the complex situation you fell into as it seems the dinosaurs and creatures you encounter are also victims of the mercenaries' ambitions. The choice is yours: engage in relentless combat, prioritizing brute violence, or study the wildlife to uncover the island's secrets, and <strong>forge unlikely alliances</strong> in your quest for survival.<br><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Immersive and <strong>visually stunning environment</strong>.<br></li><li><strong>Dynamic and interactive world</strong> teeming with life and ripe for exploration.<br></li><li>Engage in<strong> intense combat</strong> using a wide arsenal of customizable weapons.<br></li><li><strong>Study, fight or befriend both prehistoric and fantastical creatures</strong>.</li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1645630?t=1740070277","background_raw":"ht